#: casca/help_content.py:39
msgid "Websites, turned into apps. No fuss."
msgstr "Situs web, diubah menjadi aplikasi. Tanpa ribet."

#: casca/help_content.py:41
msgid ""
"Casca turns any address into a GNOME app: icon in the menu, its own window, "
"no leftover browser bar. This guide covers every option on the creation "
"screen."
msgstr ""
"Casca mengubah alamat apa pun menjadi aplikasi GNOME: ikon di menu, jendela "
"sendiri, tanpa bilah peramban yang tersisa. Panduan ini mencakup setiap opsi "
"di layar pembuatan."

#: casca/help_content.py:44
msgid "First app"
msgstr "Aplikasi pertama"

#: casca/help_content.py:45
msgid "Presets"
msgstr "Preset"

